Description: Enchant items to give them magical abilities
ActualRequirements: Enchant an item at an enchanting table

Description: Build some bookshelves for your enchanting table
ActualRequirements: Obtain a bookshelf

Description: Obtain a full stack of bottles of enchanting
Obtain Power V
ActualRequirements: Obtain Power V on any item (Bow or Enchanted Book)

Description: Obtain Infinity on a bow
Obtain Efficiency V
ActualRequirements: Obtain Efficiency V on any item

Description: Obtain Fortune III
ActualRequirements: Obtain Fortune III on any item

Description: Use a Silk Touch enchanted pickaxe to obtain diamond ore as a block
ActualRequirements: Obtain Diamond Ore or Deepslate Diamond Ore

Description: Obtain Sharpness V
Obtain Smite V
Obtain Bane of Arthropods V
Have a diamond sword with Fire Aspect II
Enchant a wooden sword with Sharpness V. Not really the best weapon, but it could be a minor annoyance to someone
Deal eight hearts of damage in a single blow
ActualRequirements: Deal at least eight hearts of damage with any melee attack

Description: Deal 16 hearts of damage in a single blow
ActualRequirements: Deal at least sixteen hearts of damage with any melee attack

Description: Shoot three arrows at once with a crossbow
ActualRequirements: Shoot a crossbow with Multishot

Description: Fire a crossbow as rapidly as possible
ActualRequirements: Shoot a crossbow with Quick Charge III

Description: Kill five unique mobs with one crossbow shot
Turn your trident into a boomerang by getting Loyalty on it
Use Riptide to give yourself a boost
ActualRequirements: Use a Riptide-enchanted trident while in water or rain

Description: Obtain Channeling on a trident
Strike a Villager with lightning
Obtain boots enchanted with Feather Falling
Obtain all protection related enchantments
ActualRequirements: Obtain the following enchantments on any items: Protection, Fire Protection, Blast Protection and Projectile Protection

Description: Obtain Knockback and Punch enchantments
ActualRequirements: Obtain Knockback and Punch on any non-book item(s)

Description: Obtain every water related enchantment
ActualRequirements: Obtain Respiration, Aqua Affinity and Depth Strider on any non-book item(s)

Description: Obtain every fire related enchantment
ActualRequirements: Obtain Fire Protection, Fire Aspect and Flame on any non-book item(s)

Description: Find the Swift Sneak enchantment on an Enchanted Book in an Ancient City
ActualRequirements: Obtain an Enchanted Book with Swift Sneak on it

Description: Sneak and sprint on sculk with Speed II while wearing Swift Sneak III leggings. Try saying that six times swiftly
Obtain the Soul Speed enchantment from a Bastion or bartering with Piglins
ActualRequirements: Obtain Soul Speed on either boots or an Enchanted Book

Description: Get every enchantment throughout your enchanting career
ActualRequirements:
Obtain the following enchantments on any items: Protection, Fire Protection, Feather Falling, Blast Protection, Projectile Protection, Respiration, Aqua Affinity, Thorns, 
Swift Sneak, Depth Strider, Frost Walker, Soul Speed, Curse of Binding, Sharpness, Smite, Bane of Arthropods, Knockback, Fire Aspect, Looting, Sweeping Edge, Efficiency, Silk Touch, 
Unbreaking, Fortune, Power, Punch, Flame, Infinity, Lure, Luck of the Sea, Loyalty, Riptide, Impaling, Channeling, Quick Charge, Piercing, Multishot, Mending, 
and Curse of Vanishing.

Description: Get every enchantment at its max level throughout your enchanting career
ActualRequirements:
Obtain the following enchantments on any items: Protection IV, Fire Protection IV, Feather Falling IV, Blast Protection IV, Projectile Protection IV, Respiration III, 
Aqua Affinity, Thorns III, Swift Sneak III, Depth Strider III, Frost Walker II, Soul Speed III, Curse of Binding, Sharpness V, Smite V, Bane of Arthropods V, Knockback II, Fire Aspect II, 
Looting III, Sweeping Edge III, Efficiency V, Silk Touch, Unbreaking III, Fortune III, Power V, Punch II, Flame, Infinity, Lure III, Luck of the Sea III, Loyalty III, Riptide III, 
Impaling V, Channeling, Quick Charge III, Piercing IV, Multishot, Mending, and Curse of Vanishing

Description: Craft an anvil
ActualRequirements: Obtain an anvil

Description: Get a stack of regular, chipped and damaged Anvils
Obtain both types of curses
ActualRequirements: Obtain Curses of Binding and Vanishing on any item(s)

Description: Wear a carved pumpkin enchanted with Curse of Binding
Using Frost Walker boots, walk on frozen water over a deep ocean
ActualRequirements: Step on Frosted Ice while wearing Frost Walker boots and in any Deep Ocean biome

Description: Name your Diamond Sword 'Diamond Edge'
ActualRequirements: Hold the named item in your mainhand

Description: Name your Bow 'Terminator'
ActualRequirements: Hold the named item in your mainhand

Description: Name your Trident with Loyalty III and Channeling 'Mjolnir'
ActualRequirements: Hold the named item in your mainhand

Description: Obtain Mending on an item
Create a pickaxe with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Diamond or Netherite Pickaxe enchanted with: Efficiency V, Unbreaking III, Mending, and either Fortune III or Silk Touch

Description: Create a shovel with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Diamond or Netherite Shovel enchanted with: Efficiency V, Unbreaking III, Mending, and either Fortune III or Silk Touch

Description: Create a axe with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements:
Obtain a Diamond or Netherite Axe enchanted with: Sharpness V OR Smite V OR Bane of Arthropods V, Efficiency V, Unbreaking III, Mending, 
and either Fortune III or Silk Touch

Description: Create a hoe with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Diamond or Netherite Hoe enchanted with: Efficiency V, Unbreaking III, Mending, and either Fortune III or Silk Touch

Description: Create a sword with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements:
Obtain a Diamond or Netherite Sword enchanted with: Sharpness V OR Smite V OR Bane of Arthropods V, Knockback II, Fire Aspect II, Looting III, Unbreaking III, 
Sweeping Edge III and Mending

Description: Create a bow with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Bow enchanted with: Power V, Punch II, Flame, Unbreaking III, and either Infinity or Mending

Description: Create a crossbow with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Crossbow enchanted with: Quick Charge III, Unbreaking III and Mending, and then either Piercing IV or Multishot

Description: Create a full suit of armor with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements:
Obtain the following items with the following enchantments:
Diamond or Netherite Helmet: Any Protection IV, Unbreaking III, Mending, Aqua Affinity, and Respiration III.
Diamond or Netherite Chestplate: Any Protection IV, Unbreaking III, Mending, and Thorns III.
Diamond or Netherite Leggings: Any Protection IV, Unbreaking III, Mending and Swift Sneak III.
Diamond or Netherite Boots: Any Protection IV, Unbreaking III, Mending, Feather Falling IV, Soul Speed III and either Depth Strider III or Frost Walker II.

Description: Create a fishing rod with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Fishing Rod enchanted with: Lure III, Luck of the Sea III, Unbreaking III and Mending

Description: Create a trident with all possible enchantments at max level
ActualRequirements: Obtain a Trident enchanted with: Impaling V, Unbreaking III, Mending, and then either Riptide III, or Loyalty III and Channeling
